item.title: What files to change Ip & Name?
item.dc:creator: @11j123 11j123
item.description:
@11j123 wrote:

Server side: Server.java to change the IP and port the server listens on.
Client side: Go to client.java (most likely) to change the IP

For the login message, I suggest you search in your server folder for what the message is, then you can change it, or add new ones.
